nd gleichermaßen eine Darstellung der wichtigsten Methoden der Diskurslinguistik wie ein Kompendium der aktuellen methodologischen Diskussion.  aWithin linguistics, discourse linguistics has now become established as a sub-discipline dealing with supratextual meaning relations and historically and culturally based knowledge. A large number of individual studies have been presented and the theoretical discussion is well advanced. What is still lacking, however, is a soundly-based methodology, which is where this volume comes in. The contributors present and discuss various investigative procedures.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aDiscourse analysisvCongresses. 0aGerman languagexDiscourse analysisvCongresses. 4aDiskurslingistik. 4aMethodologie. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aDiscourse Analysis, Methodology.1 aAlbert, Georg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAngermüller, Johannes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBubenhofer, Noah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBusse, Dietrich, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFix, Ulla, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFraas, Claudia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJohnson, Sally, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKonerding, Klaus-Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeier, Stefan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMilani, Tommaso M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPentzold, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRoth, Kerst